Telegram Bot with AI Features 🤖✨
Bot Preview

A multifunctional Telegram bot built with Python and aiogram 3 that provides various AI-powered features including random facts, ChatGPT interface, celebrity conversations, and quizzes.

Features 🌟
Random Fact (/random) - Get interesting facts with AI-generated content

ChatGPT Interface (/gpt) - Directly interact with OpenAI's ChatGPT

Celebrity Chat (/talk) - Have conversations with historical figures

Quiz Game (/quiz) - Test your knowledge in various topics with score tracking

Technologies Used 🛠️
Python 3.10+

aiogram 3 (asynchronous Telegram Bot API)

OpenAI API (GPT-3.5-turbo)

Asynchronous programming (asyncio)

Project Structure 📂
my_bot/
├── app.py                 # Entry point
├── config.py              # Configuration
├── misc.py                # Configuration start and shutdown
├── handlers/              # Command handlers
│   ├── command.py         # /start command
│   ├── random_fact.py     # /random command
│   ├── gpt_interface.py   # /gpt command
│   ├── talk.py            # /talk command
│   └── quiz.py            # /quiz command
├── keyboards/             # Bot keyboards
│   └── keyboard.py        # Shared keyboards
├── resources/             # media files
└── utils/                 # Utility functions
    ├── chatgpt.py         # OpenAI API wrapper
    └── images.py          # Image handling
Setup Instructions 🚀
Prerequisites
Python 3.10 or later

Telegram Bot Token from @BotFather

OpenAI API key

Installation
Clone the repository:

bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-telegram-bot.git
cd ai-telegram-bot
Install dependencies:

bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Create a .env file in the project root:

env
BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key

Run the bot:

bash
python app.py
Usage Guide 📖
Start the bot with /start command

Choose from available options:

/random - Get random facts

/gpt - Chat with AI (reply to any message)

/talk - Talk with historical figures

/quiz - Play knowledge quiz

Contribution 🤝
Contributions are welcome! Please open an issue or submit a pull request for any improvements.


Enjoy using the bot! For any questions, please open an issue in this repository.